A video of a Mercedes Benz crashing into a security guard has surfaced on social media. The incident allegedly happened in Morningside in Johannesburg on Sunday afternoon. In the video, a white Mercedes Benz can be seen driving at high speeds towards the security guard, who is sitting next to a wall. The Benz then hits the security guard and he can be seen flying in the air. Following that the car continues to move and hits a pole before coming to a standstill. The security guard miraculously manages to get up and can be seen trying to walk. WATCH VIDEO BELOW: 